{"tid":1632063,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"10月7  十八區開花  攪黨鐵  停裝修","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:36:42.000Z","uid":16291,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"a36cec3dbf5e474161319159a40d708877948475","tid":1632063,"uid":16291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:02.000Z","msg":"長話短說<br />\n大家都要盡做，但要做得漂亮！<br />\n黨鐵呢幾個月同政府同流合污，大家有目共睹<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請勇武對準政權，亦間接有助之後既罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">裝修係大快人心，但係國際未理解，<br />\n容易失去其他國家支持</span><br />\n<br />\n和理非，請繼續做靚文宣<br />\n繼續國際戰線<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">18區！18區！18區！<br />\n單一戰場容易比對方有足夠人手應付。</span><br />\n<br />\n不分化、不篤灰<br />\n不抹黑、不割蓆"},{"pid":"9e03c608f01343205b0dd18fee39991fc1cb92ef","tid":1632063,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:43.000Z","msg":"［重整旗鼓］和勇再connect<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631941</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a3e20114a129a2ca7189f5eeee4f91ee3fa7bae2","tid":1632063,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」繞過立法會直接立法，公然破壞香港法治制度。<br />\n三罷公投，投票表達意向！<br />\n<br />\n截至10月6日下午4點，我們收到超過32,000份有效回應。感謝大家支持，請繼續廣傳，全家總動員，一齊填問卷，我哋要更多，更多支持！<br />\n<br />\n請登入 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=6e30f210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a> 或掃QR code填寫問卷。<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government turns a blind eye to Hong Kongers&rsquo; demands. Last week, the government passed (introduced?) a new emergency law banning facial coverings. Such act is an almost complete destruction of the judicial independence and the rule of law in Hong Kong. The time has come and we must speak up. Tell us your opinions on general strike. It&rsquo;s now or never.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\nGoogle form link : <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=6e30f210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVmL21x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVmL21x.jpg&h=b4f9574f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L1B4y8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL1B4y8d.jpg&h=6be29586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"394264c6b4130585a1210c3fd638a1d7f19d490c","tid":1632063,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYtuLaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYtuLaR.jpg&h=f5ef1ebb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cd811a8b2bbc32634ebdc15461a7c5b4b98ea43","tid":1632063,"uid":16291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:52.000Z","msg":"合勇合作啊！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n大家都做得好好！！"},{"pid":"b439ba612e26ff2e25a33e1a48a8119f922ac70f","tid":1632063,"uid":16291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">辛苦晒勇武！</span>"},{"pid":"1c52a8ba44b3d3f0ec4308ac8a09ce1de5016cef","tid":1632063,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"[遍地落區公投] 連登已被嚴重滲透，任何風向公投都唔應該再係連登搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d21586edbffc96cbf3f7305622ed4cea94b85d66","tid":1632063,"uid":16291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">多謝和理非！</span>"},{"pid":"23d51c0451b6ae15b2d6e0af286396b873a1b22e","tid":1632063,"ui